  67:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_spi.c ****           bidirectional receive mode (MSTR=1, BIDIMODE=1, BIDIOE=0), to ensure that the SPI
  68:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_spi.c ****           does not initiate a new transfer the following procedure has to be respected:
